## Kafka
Kafka__BootstrapServers=localhost:9092
Kafka__ConsumerGroupId=hammer-support

## Onbid API
Onbid__ServiceKey=YOUR_SERVICE_KEY_HERE

## Molit API (same data.go.kr key)
Molit__ServiceKey=YOUR_SERVICE_KEY_HERE

## PostgreSQL
ConnectionStrings__DefaultConnection=Host=localhost;Port=5432;Database=hammer_support;Username=postgres;Password=postgres

## FCM (Firebase Cloud Messaging)
Fcm__CredentialPath=firebase-credentials.json
